## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8391-105">A conta de entidade de usuário não é persistida quando ele é criado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-105">The user principal account is not persisted when it is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8391-106">Para salvar a conta, chame o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> método.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-106">To save the account, call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8391-107">O exemplo de código a seguir conecta-se ao domínio LDAP "fabrikam.com" com o nome de usuário e senha são inicializados no <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> construtor "administrador" e "securelyStoredPassword".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-107">The following code example connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username and password initialized in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor to "administrator" and "securelyStoredPassword."</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8391-108">As propriedades definidas no exemplo, como o endereço de email e de nome de usuário, são criadas sob o contêiner especificado no <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> construtor: "CN = Users, DC = fabrikam, DC = com."</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-108">The properties set in the example, such as user name and email address, are created under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor: "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span>  
  
```  
  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                         ContextType.Domain,  
                                         "fabrikam.com",   
                                         "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",  
                                         "administrator",   
                                         "securelyStoredPassword");   
  
UserPrincipal usr = new UserPrincipal(ctx);  
  
usr.Name = "Jim Daly";  
usr.Description = "This is the user account for Jim Daly";  
usr.EmailAddress = "jimdaly@fabrikam.com";  
usr.SetPassword("securelyStoredPassword");  
usr.Save();  
  
usr.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();   
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8391-160">O código a seguir se conecta ao armazenamento do computador local.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-160">The following code connects to the local computer store.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8391-161">Como as credenciais não são especificadas no <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> construtor, as credenciais da execução do usuário que o thread atual são usadas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-161">Since the credentials are not specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor, the credentials of the user running the current thread are used.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8391-162">Uma pesquisa é executada para localizar o usuário que tem o SamAccountName "Convidado".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-162">A search is performed to find the user who has SamAccountName "Guest".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8391-163">Se o usuário for encontrado, uma verificação é executada para determinar se essa conta de usuário está habilitada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-163">If the user is found, a check is performed to determine whether this user's account is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8391-164">Se a conta não estiver habilitada, ele permite que o código de exemplo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8391-164">If the account is not enabled, the example code enables it.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Machine);  
  
UserPrincipal usr = UserPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx,   
                                           IdentityType.SamAccountName,   
                                           "Guest");  
  
if(usr != null)  
{  
    if (usr.Enabled == false)  
        usr.Enabled = true;  
  
    usr.Save();  
    usr.Dispose();  
}  
ctx.Dispose();   
```
